### App Scholar - API Requests

## Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

## ===== AUTHENTICATION =====

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

## ===== ALUNOS =====

### List all alunos
GET {{baseUrl}}/alunos
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get aluno by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/alunos/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get aluno by matrícula
GET {{baseUrl}}/alunos/matricula/MAT001
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create aluno (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/alunos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "nome": "João Pedro",
  "matricula": "MAT003",
  "email": "joao@student.com",
  "telefone": "(11) 99999-9999",
  "cpf": "123.456.789-00",
  "data_nascimento": "2004-05-15"
}

### Update aluno (admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/alunos/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "nome": "João Silva Updated",
  "email": "joao.updated@email.com"
}

### Delete aluno (admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/alunos/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

## ===== DISCIPLINAS =====

### List all disciplinas
GET {{baseUrl}}/disciplinas
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get disciplina by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/disciplinas/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create disciplina (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/disciplinas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "nome": "Programação Web",
  "codigo": "PROG101",
  "carga_horaria": 60,
  "professor_id": 1
}

### Update disciplina (admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/disciplinas/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "nome": "Programação Web Avançada",
  "carga_horaria": 80
}

### Delete disciplina (admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/disciplinas/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

## ===== BOLETIM =====

### Get boletim by matrícula
GET {{baseUrl}}/boletim/MAT001
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Add/Update grade (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/boletim/grades
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "aluno_id": 1,
  "disciplina_id": 1,
  "nota1": 8.5,
  "nota2": 7.5
}

## ===== HEALTH CHECK =====

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health
